title: This apartment will rent FAST! Be the first to live in it!!! Only One!
map_address: 47201 Mission Falls Ct near Warm Springs
posting_body: ['Welcome to Palmia!', 'A resort-style community for active adults.', 'Discover the comfortable new home you’ve been looking for at our luxury 55+ apartments.', 'Our pet-friendly one- and two-bedroom apartments are brand new and feature designer details and high-grade appliances.', 'We have fun community amenities and activities in one of the most desirable locations in the region.', 'Enjoy the sun poolside, bond over the outdoor fireplace, catch a flick at our resident movie theater or simply relax at your new home.', 'A life of serenity and recreation waits for you at Palmia.', 'Be a part of our smoke-free senior community in the Bay Area and experience the best of Fremont senior living.', '-Landscaped Outdoor Common Areas', '-Ample Bike Storage', '-In-home Whirlpool Washer and Dryer', '-Balconies and Private Patios', '-Electric Range and Microwave Oven', '-Epicurean Kitchen for Resident Cooking Classes', '-Key Fob System to Access Building', '-Smoke-Free Community', '-Barbeques and Alfresco Dining Areas', '-24-Hour Package Retreval for your deliveries', '-Designer Carpet in Bedrooms', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Ask for Apartment Home #1321', 'Advertized rent price includes 3 months free and considering a 12 month lease.']
